      • readResolve

        private java.lang.Object readResolve()
                              throws java.io.ObjectStreamException
        Reads from external source the ownership object. If ownership object is null, places into allInstancesHm this ownership object's name which keys this object. It then adds this object to the ownership arraylist. If there is an ownership object it returns it.
